    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 6.24,
      "end": 11.16,
      "text": "For more information or to volunteer, please visit LibraVox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 11.88,
      "end": 15.78,
      "text": "Recorded by Christine Doer, the known as Assa, Florida.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 18.56,
      "end": 22.08,
      "text": "Esaups Fables, the farmer, and fortune.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 23.62,
      "end": 28.9,
      "text": "A farmer was plowing one day on his farm when he turned up a pot of golden coins with",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 28.9,
      "end": 29.44,
      "text": "his plow.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 30.5,
      "end": 36.38,
      "text": "He was ever enjoyed at his discovery, and from that time forth made an offering daily at",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 36.38,
      "end": 37.98,
      "text": "the shrine of the goddess of the earth.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 38.98,
      "end": 45.82,
      "text": "Fortune was displeased at this, and came to him and said, My man, why do you give earth",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 45.82,
      "end": 48.34,
      "text": "the credit for the gift which I bestowed upon you?",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 48.82,
      "end": 51.42,
      "text": "You never thought of thanking me for your good luck.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 52.04,
      "end": 54.96,
      "text": "But should you be unlucky enough to lose what you have gained?",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-013",
      "start": 54.96,
      "end": 61.0,
      "text": "I know very well that I, Fortune, should then come in for all the blame.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-014",
      "start": 62.22,
      "end": 65.06,
      "text": "Show gratitude, where gratitude is due.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-015",
      "start": 66.38,
      "end": 68.94,
      "text": "End of the Farmer and Fortune.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
